{"tid":1131883,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[FF] 如果你係香港國總統，你會選擇邊到作為首都？","createTime":"2019-04-30T02:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T03:53:00.000Z","uid":206224,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9850ba7704e422299d54c814a45820cfdc1be819","tid":1131883,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:42:12.000Z","msg":"選擇首都嘅因素可以包括：<br />\n- 歷史<br />\n- 經濟金融<br />\n- 政府、立法、司法機關所在地<br />\n- 國防戰略<br />\n- 文化<br />\n- 人口<br />\n- 空間<br />\n<br />\n以中環金鐘為例，有強烈嘅歷史意義，又係各大機關同埋經濟重心地；不過選址太近大銀行企業嘅話又會比人有種官商勾結嘅感覺，而且空間狹窄，好難再作未來大規模規劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6784c9b97f34222275e2c83c0dd839a5775a7fc","tid":1131883,"uid":206224,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"比著係我我就會大刀闊斧發展啟德，破舊立新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503c26574a861e459b1ed9798b52056d2cb5aed2","tid":1131883,"uid":225846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:45:08.000Z","msg":"我屋企 改埋做帝國 thanks"},{"pid":"bccf8a1173279be983a2bf8652f06e35bdc209d1","tid":1131883,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"西環"},{"pid":"c441a65c966f97bde3891cdab7fc12ecb90f34ea","tid":1131883,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bccf8a1173279be983a2bf8652f06e35bdc209d1","tid":1131883,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"西環"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:46:49.000Z","msg":"共匪"},{"pid":"769c8ee63cfcd802b4ca9d86ac3585afba846607","tid":1131883,"uid":48631,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"首咩都呀,你會唔會問新加坡首都喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823347ef2ae05a26e809cbf073cb8f7a673a5aa1","tid":1131883,"uid":114023,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:5